to want to see him.

35
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:30,560
Xiao.

36
00:01:31,359 --> 00:01:32,120
Xiao.

37
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,319
Xiao.

38
00:01:33,799 --> 00:01:35,120
Come out and see me.

39
00:01:35,799 --> 00:01:36,480
Xiao,

40
00:01:36,799 --> 00:01:37,920
